mile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a29ec555c323093463e5db21eb2936867846335","tid":1174944,"uid":59662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4914a6b97dd2bb769b7916a8300d9ea9b974bbe","tid":1174944,"uid":59662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"用complex number做座標，tn係第n日嘅增量<br />\n<br />\nt1=1<br />\nt2=(+-)i<br />\nt3=(+-)2<br />\nt4=(+-)3i<br />\nt5=(+-)4<br />\ntn=(+-) i^(n-1) (n-1)<br />\n<br />\nCoordinate at day n = t1+t2+t3+...+tn<br />\n<br />\nSum all odd terms for Real part of coordinate<br />\nsum(t(2n-1))=1 + (+-)2 + (+-)4 + ... + (+-) 2(n-1) = 1 + sum or subtraction of even numbers &lt;&gt; 0<br />\n<br />\nsum(t(2n))=1 + (+-)2 + (+-)4 + ... + (+-) 2(n-1) = 1 + sum or subtraction of even numbers &lt;&gt; 0<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇樓主話原點係(1,0) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:30:21.000Z","msg":"copy錯唔駛理sum(t(2n))果句"},{"pid":"4de76f67e87435dac97c6364efcaf34aa14d0ed3","tid":1174944,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"第二日1,1就no sol."},{"pid":"8c3b09a613e4e8c49f8f4a55d7b715a5f86a79c1","tid":1174944,"uid":231912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4914a6b97dd2bb769b7916a8300d9ea9b974bbe","tid":1174944,"uid":59662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"用complex number做座標，tn係第n日嘅增量<br />\n<br />\nt1=1<br />\nt2=(+-)i<br />\nt3=(+-)2<br />\nt4=(+-)3i<br />\nt5=(+-)4<br />\ntn=(+-) i^(n-1) (n-1)<br />\n<br />\nCoordinate at day n = t1+t2+t3+...+tn<br />\n<br />\nSum all odd terms for Real part of coordinate<br />\nsum(t(2n-1))=1 + (+-)2 + (+-)4 + ... + (+-) 2(n-1) = 1 + sum or subtraction of even numbers &lt;&gt; 0<br />\n<br />\nsum(t(2n))=1 + (+-)2 + (+-)4 + ... + (+-) 2(n-1) = 1 + sum or subtraction of even numbers &lt;&gt; 0<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇樓主話原點係(1,0) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif